{"tid":2217933,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–抗生素為人類與細菌的戰場","createTime":"2020-09-25T22:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T16:42:13.000Z","uid":38861,"like":52,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"68d4c8ee871426ef72bd3560ca20c1953361fc68","tid":2217933,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T22:52:28.000Z","msg":"抗生素是其中一種應付細菌或微生物的手段，以Virginiamycin M2(VM2)這抗生素為例，它能夠與細菌的核糖體（Ribosome)結合，從而抑制細菌的生長及繁殖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/peU5f6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpeU5f6c.jpg&h=8e5ecea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為應對抗生素的襲擊，細菌亦會發展出不同的機制作出制衡。同樣以VM2作為例子，細菌會生產一隻名為VatA酵素，能夠有效對VM2進行改造。<br />\n<br />\n被改造的VM2再也無法合併及阻礙Ribosome功能，細菌亦得以繼續無阻繁殖，展示出抗藥性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）最近，有科學家應用名為Modular Synthesis的技術進行應對(Ref1)。<br />\n簡單來說，Modular Synthesis就把化學物當作是砌LEGO一樣，能夠任意在短時間內改組化學物的各個部位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QGQ8dSV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQGQ8dSV.jpg&h=1aa99602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如圖中所示，化學物各顏色部位均能轉變成其相應顏色的組件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）經過一輪的驗證後，科學家發現細菌VatA酵素會在VM2某部位(C14)進行改造，但箇中過程將會與VM2另一個位置(C4)進行觸碰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvFsuri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvFsuri.jpg&h=e2f2fad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基於這點，科學家特意在C4部位裝上一大串臃腫的化學結構，促使細菌VatA酵素無法與VM2進行互動的同時，亦能確保人為改造的VM2能夠使細菌的Ribosome功能受阻。<br />\n<br />\n當然，並不難想像細菌會隨著時間的增長發展出另一種新穎的應對方法，到時候科學家會否重用Modular Synthesis技倆應對，或者發展出一道一勞永逸的方法，就有待我們細心等候了。<br />\n<br />\n暫時來說，這場道高一尺、魔高一丈的遊戲，應該還要持續好一段的時間。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"red\">like</span>以及<span class=\"green\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=1e89161f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=5a8d5766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2761-3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-020-2761-3&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=09bb1ea7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2761-3</a>"},{"pid":"f2c6376697e58fedc8edaab27e1b2854507cd378","tid":2217933,"uid":58642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7476670c0cfd3ea44b7b5fe2a0fd1b7b57f60d","tid":2217933,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:40:13.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3a42b0cc0deff52946a27047a8fc1bb9caec7749","tid":2217933,"uid":54323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:48:25.000Z","msg":"一日兩帖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99